

The ISSS (Salvadoran Social Security Institute) pharmacy system has improved efficiency, particularly through home delivery for chronic patients and digital initiatives, achieving high patient satisfaction. Key services include automated, properly packaged, and labeled prescriptions that enhance medication adherence while reducing travel costs for beneficiaries. 
