Key Aspects of the ISSS Pharmacy System:
Home Delivery System: Implemented in collaboration with Correos El Salvador, this service offers nationwide coverage for repeat prescriptions.
Patient Satisfaction: Studies show high satisfaction with medication delivery services, with roughly 64.5% of patients reporting proper labeling and 59.1% reporting proper packaging.
Adherence and Efficiency: Over 63% of patients felt the service enhanced their ability to adhere to medication regimes, significantly improving service delivery.
Digital Transformation: The system is part of a broader, healthcare professional-backed shift towards electronic systems, which are viewed as opportunities to apply clinical expertise. 
